<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex,nofollow" />
  <title>Research — Stage 2 retrieval (admin)</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: system-ui, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem 2rem; background: #0f1419; color: #e6edf3; line-height: 1.45; font-size: 0.92rem; }
    .rs2-top { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .rs2-top a { color: #58a6ff; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; }
    .rs2-top a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    h1 { font-size: 1.2rem; margin: 0 0 0.35rem; font-weight: 600; text-align: center; }
    p.hint { font-size: 0.82rem; color: #8b949e; margin: 0 0 1rem; max-width: 46rem; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; text-align: center; }
    label { display: block; font-size: 0.78rem; color: #8b949e; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
    select, button { font: inherit; border-radius: 8px; }
    select { padding: 0.45rem 0.55rem; border: 1px solid #30363d; background: #0d1117; color: #e6edf3; max-width: 22rem; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; }
    .row { margin-bottom: 0.85rem; max-width: 44rem; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
    .toolbar { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 1rem 0; }
    button { padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border: 1px solid #388bfd; background: rgba(56, 139, 253, 0.2); color: #e6edf3; cursor: pointer; }
    button:disabled { opacity: 0.5; cursor: not-allowed; }
    button.secondary { border-color: #30363d; background: #21262d; }
    #rs2-progress { min-height: 1.5rem; font-size: 0.82rem; color: #8ab4ff; margin: 0.5rem 0; text-align: center; max-width: 52rem; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; line-height: 1.4; }
    .rs2-stack-card { max-width: 52rem; margin: 0 auto 1rem; padding: 0.85rem 1rem; border: 1px solid #30363d; border-radius: 10px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2); }
    .rs2-stack-card h2 { font-size: 0.85rem; margin: 0 0 0.5rem; color: #8b949e; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
    #rs2-stack { max-height: min(55vh, 28rem); overflow-y: auto; font-size: 0.8rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.65rem; }
    .stack-item { border-left: 3px solid #484f58; padding: 0.35rem 0 0.35rem 0.65rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0; }
    .stack-item.stack-init { border-left-color: #8b949e; }
    .stack-item.stack-openalex { border-left-color: #58a6ff; }
    .stack-item.stack-semantic_scholar { border-left-color: #a371f7; }
    .stack-item.stack-dedupe { border-left-color: #d4a72c; }
    .stack-item.stack-score { border-left-color: #3fb950; }
    .stack-item.stack-trim { border-left-color: #f0883e; }
    .stack-title { font-weight: 600; color: #c9d1d9; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
    .stack-step-meta { font-size: 0.72rem; color: #6e7681; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; margin: 0 0 0.35rem; }
    .stack-bullets { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.1rem; color: #8b949e; line-height: 1.45; }
    .stack-bullets li { margin-bottom: 0.15rem; }
    .rs2-trace-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.72rem; margin-top: 0.35rem; }
    .rs2-trace-table th, .rs2-trace-table td { border-bottom: 1px solid #30363d; padding: 0.4rem 0.35rem; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; }
    .rs2-trace-table th { color: #8b949e; font-weight: 600; }
    .rs2-trace-table td.trace-detail { color: #8b949e; line-height: 1.4; max-width: 36rem; }
    .rs2-trace-table .trace-line { margin-bottom: 0.2rem; }
    #rs2-status { min-height: 1.25rem; font-size: 0.85rem; color: #8b949e; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; text-align: center; }
    #rs2-status.err { color: #f85149; }
    #rs2-status.ok { color: #3fb950; }
    .warn-banner { background: rgba(187,128,9,0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(187,128,9,0.45); color: #d4a72c; padding: 0.75rem 1rem; border-radius: 8px; max-width: 56rem; margin: 0 auto 1rem; font-size: 0.85rem; }
    .err-banner { background: rgba(248,81,73,0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(248,81,73,0.35); color: #f85149; }
    .card { max-width: 56rem; margin: 0 auto 1.25rem; padding: 1rem 1.25rem; border: 1px solid #30363d; border-radius: 10px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); }
    .card h2 { font-size: 1rem; margin: 0 0 0.75rem; color: #c9d1d9; }
    .stats-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(11rem, 1fr)); gap: 0.5rem 1rem; font-size: 0.82rem; }
    .stats-grid strong { color: #8b949e; display: block; font-size: 0.72rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.02em; }
    .chart-block { margin-top: 1rem; }
    .bar-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.35rem; font-size: 0.78rem; }
    .bar-label { width: 12rem; flex-shrink: 0; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap; color: #c9d1d9; }
    .bar-track { flex: 1; height: 1rem; background: #21262d; border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; }
    .bar-fill { height: 100%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #388bfd, #58a6ff); border-radius: 4px; min-width: 2px; }
    .bar-count { width: 2.5rem; text-align: right; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; color: #8b949e; }
    .hist-row { display: flex; align-items: flex-end; gap: 2px; height: 120px; margin-top: 0.5rem; }
    .hist-col { flex: 1; min-width: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: flex-end; align-items: center; }
    .hist-bar { width: 100%; background: #388bfd; border-radius: 2px 2px 0 0; min-height: 2px; }
    .hist-year { font-size: 0.65rem; color: #8b949e; transform: rotate(-45deg); white-space: nowrap; margin-top: 0.25rem; }
    .table-wrap { max-width: 64rem; margin: 0 auto; overflow: auto; max-height: 60vh; border: 1px solid #30363d; border-radius: 8px; }
    table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.78rem; }
    th, td { border-bottom: 1px solid #30363d; padding: 0.45rem 0.5rem; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; }
    th { background: #161b22; color: #8b949e; position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 1; cursor: pointer; user-select: none; }
    th:hover { color: #c9d1d9; }
    th.sorted-asc::after { content: ' ▲'; font-size: 0.65rem; }
    th.sorted-desc::after { content: ' ▼'; font-size: 0.65rem; }
    td.num { font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; text-align: right; }
    tr:nth-child(even) { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); }
    .rs2-hidden { display: none !important; }
    .toolbar a.primary-link {
      display: inline-block; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #238636;
      background: rgba(35, 134, 54, 0.2); color: #e6edf3; font: inherit; text-decoration: none;
    }
    .toolbar a.primary-link:hover { filter: brightness(1.08); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="rs2-top">
    <a href="/admin/research-stage1">← Stage 1 plan</a>
    ·
    <a href="/admin/research-stage1-timing">Bedrock run times</a>
  </div>
  <h1>Research — Stage 2 corpus retrieval</h1>
  <p class="hint">Uses your <strong>latest saved Stage 1 plan</strong> from the server. Retrieves from OpenAlex and Semantic Scholar, deduplicates, scores, and trims the corpus. Polite pool: <code>OPENALEX_MAILTO</code> or your signed-in email. Optional S2 rate limits: <code>S2_API_KEY</code> or <code>SEMANTIC_SCHOLAR_API_KEY</code>. After a run, <strong>Per-query API trace</strong> (below) mirrors what is stored in <code>statistics_json.query_trace</code> for that saved corpus. Python stderr lines (including <code>LOG.info</code> for each S2/OpenAlex call) are forwarded to the app server log stream as <code>[research-stage2:py]</code>. Requires <code>python3</code> and <code>stage2_retrieval.py</code> on the server.</p>

  <div class="row">
    <label for="rs2-type">Corpus size profile (Stage 1 project type)</label>
    <select id="rs2-type">
      <option value="assignment">assignment (30–50 papers)</option>
      <option value="dissertation" selected>dissertation (200–500 papers)</option>
      <option value="conference">conference (50–150 papers)</option>
      <option value="journal">journal (100–300 papers)</option>
    </select>
  </div>

  <div class="toolbar">
    <button type="button" id="rs2-run">Run retrieval</button>
    <button type="button" class="secondary" id="rs2-load-saved">Load last saved corpus</button>
  </div>
  <div id="rs2-status" aria-live="polite"></div>
  <div id="rs2-progress" aria-live="polite"></div>

  <div id="rs2-stack-wrap" class="rs2-stack-card rs2-hidden">
    <h2>What ran</h2>
    <p class="hint" style="text-align:left;margin:0 0 0.5rem;font-size:0.76rem;">Step-by-step volumes: documents fetched, search strings, concept filters, then dedupe, scoring, and trim.</p>
    <div id="rs2-stack"></div>
  </div>

  <div id="rs2-warn-zero" class="warn-banner rs2-hidden"></div>
  <div id="rs2-warn-err" class="warn-banner err-banner rs2-hidden"></div>

  <div id="rs2-results" class="rs2-hidden">
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Summary</h2>
      <div id="rs2-stats" class="stats-grid"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h2>Papers per construct</h2>
      <div id="rs2-chart-constructs" class="chart-block"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h2>Year distribution</h2>
      <div id="rs2-chart-years" class="chart-block"></div>
    </div>

    <div id="rs2-query-trace-wrap" class="card rs2-hidden">
      <h2>Per-query API trace</h2>
      <p class="hint" style="text-align:left;margin:0 0 0.35rem;font-size:0.76rem;">Each retrieval row: OpenAlex and Semantic Scholar counts, request pages, HTTP status, and error bodies (S2 boolean queries may need simplifying if you see 4xx).</p>
      <div id="rs2-query-trace"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h2>Final corpus</h2>
      <div class="table-wrap">
        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th data-sort="relevance_score" class="sorted-desc">Relevance</th>
              <th data-sort="title">Title</th>
              <th data-sort="authors">Authors</th>
              <th data-sort="year">Year</th>
              <th data-sort="venue">Venue</th>
              <th data-sort="constructs">Constructs</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody id="rs2-tbody"></tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="toolbar">
      <a class="primary-link" href="/admin/research-stage2-enrichment">Proceed to Enrichment →</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="/js/admin-research-stage2.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
